      "content": "i see what u mean. it's just that i've heard from friends that when the demographics shift a lot, the school quality usually drops pretty fast and crime goes up. it's hard not to worry about that for the kids. \n\njust to be totally honest, if i'm looking at two districts that both have high test scores, but one is 90% white and the other is 50/50 or more diverse, which one would you actually recommend to someone who prioritizes long-term stability and safety? is it safer to just stick with the more homogeneous areas to avoid those risks?",
